  Automatic trans fluid poured slowly down the carb at 2000 rpms will clean
all the carbon build up off the valves and pistons. Just SMOKES a lot, watch
out that somebody doesn't call the fire department.

ronnie

ps. Got really greasy hands, wash them with ATF, works better then soap!

